# 跨平台协作：文本统一为 LF，避免 Windows/macOS/Linux 之间 CRLF/LF 来回切换。
# 与 `.vscode/settings.json` 中 `files.eol`、Prettier 默认一致。
* text=auto eol=lf

# Windows 原生脚本若需 CRLF，取消下一行注释（本仓库以 LF 为主时可保持注释）
# *.bat text eol=crlf
# *.cmd text eol=crlf

# ---------- 常见二进制：禁止按文本做换行归一化 / diff 合并 ----------
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.webp binary
*.ico binary
*.icns binary

*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.otf binary
*.eot binary

*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.gz binary
*.tgz binary
*.7z binary
*.rar binary

*.wasm binary
*.node binary
*.so binary
*.dylib binary
*.dll binary
*.exe binary

# 音视频（若仓库中有素材）
*.mp3 binary
*.mp4 binary
*.webm binary
*.mov binary
*.wav binary
